  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 \u0b86\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1 ? \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd- \u0bb0\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Who will be appointed for the vacant parliamentary seat? The management committee of the party will decide- Range",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "A name from the United National Party will be announced soon for Ranil Wickramasinghe's parliamentary seat.",
        "In this regard, the party's management committee chaired by President Ranil Wickramasinghe is meeting to decide, said the secretary of the party, Palitha Range Bandara.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe said this in reference to the member to be appointed to the vacant seat in the Parliament as he has accepted the post as President.",
        "The United National Party did not get any seats in the general election held on 5th August 2020.",
        "However, Ranil Wickramasinghe represented the United National Party through the only national list seat available to the party and went to the Parliament and took oath.",
        "However, following the resignation of Prime Minister Mahinda Rajapaksa due to popular protests in the country, former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa appointed Ranil Wickramasinghe as Prime Minister.",
        "Following the resignation of Gotabaya Rajapaksa, Ranil Wickramasinghe was elected as the President by a majority vote in the Parliament.",
        "Following Ranil Wickramasinghe's election as President, the seat of UNP's Ranil Wickramasinghe in Parliament has become vacant.",
        "It has not yet been decided who will be appointed for this vacancy. However, based on President Ranil Wickramasinghe's advice, the party's management committee will meet and take steps to quickly name someone to the parliament, he said."
      ],
